### Application for Police Certificate of Character - Bulk Upload

  
  

Bulk payment - Police Certificate of Character (application form information)

 

Please note that, when paying online, through the EZPAY+ payment platform, Direct Debit transactions will take five (5) business days for the payment to be approved and therefore may result in a longer processing time for the Certificate of Character. However, credit card and mMoney payment options will be approved instantly and therefore, if there are no issues with the applications, the certificates will be emailed within 48 hours. 

 

If you do not receive your certificate within the  48 hours, you may contact the Police Certificate of Character office at:

 

Telephone Numbers: 1 (246) 430-7677 or 1 (246) 228-0131

Email Address: rbpf.coc@barbados.gov.bb
